{"word":"βάναυσος","slug":"βάναυσος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n19307\" key=\"ba/nausos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">βάναυσος</orth> [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ᾰ], <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>,</foreign> (for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βαύναυσος,</foreign> from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βαῦνος, αὔω</foreign> acc. to <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4099.tlg001:187:40\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EM\">EM</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">187.40</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βαναυσία· πᾶσα τέχνη διὰ πυρός,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βαναύσων</foreign> seems to be <sense id=\"n19307.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">f.l. for</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">βαύνων</ref> </xr> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1414.tlg001:69\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Heraclit.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">All.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">69</biblScope> </bibl>):—epith. of the class of handicraftsmen or artisans, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ β.,</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">τὸ περὶ τὰς τέχνας ὧν ἄνευ πόλιν ἀδύνατον οἰκεῖσθαι</ref> </xr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg035.perseus-grc1:1291a:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\